# User Login Page with Styling

This project includes HTML and CSS code for creating a user login page with a stylish design. The login page features a form for users to input their username, email, and password. It also includes a navigation menu for easy access to different sections of the website.

## Features

-   **Background**: The background of the page is set to an engaging image of the sky, creating a visually pleasing atmosphere.
-   **Responsive Design**: The page is designed to be responsive, adapting to different screen sizes and devices.
-   **Form Styling**: The form inputs are styled to be transparent with subtle borders, enhancing the aesthetic appeal.
-   **Submit Button**: The submit button has a distinct appearance, changing color and padding on hover.
-   **Navigation Menu**: A navigation menu is included with links to various sections, providing easy navigation for users.
-   **Responsive Menu Icon**: A responsive menu icon is available for smaller screens, allowing users to toggle the navigation menu.

## Contents

-   `index.html`: The HTML file containing the structure of the user login page.
-   `loginpage.css`: The CSS file containing the styling rules for the login page and navigation menu.
-   `sky.png`: An image used as the background of the page.
-   `world-modified.webp`: An image used as the background for the navigation menu on smaller screens.

## Usage

1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Open the `index.html` file in a web browser to view the user login page.

## Customization

-   Feel free to replace the background image (`sky.png`) and navigation menu background image (`world-modified.webp`) with images of your choice.
-   Adjust the colors, fonts, and layout by modifying the CSS in the `loginpage.css` file to match your desired design.

